评投资组合的熵理论和信息价值》是本好书，作者目前也在运转一个私募。英文的可以看那些经典的量化投资论文，比如<The cross-section of expected stock returns>, <Pairs trading: performance of a relative-value arbitrage rule>, <Does the stock market overact?>, <Value and growth investing: review and update>, etc. 我自己是研究量化投资组合选择这一块的，这方面有不少文章可以推荐，比如<A New Interpretation of Information Rate>, <Optimal Gambling Systems For Favorable Games>, <Portfolio Choice and the Kelly Criterion>, etc. 
